# WORD FORGE — FINAL GAME DESIGN

---

# CORE IDEA

Word Forge is a mobile word puzzle game where players discover hidden English words using clues and a circle of letters.

It is **not** a dictionary.

It is **not** a grammar app.

It is a puzzle game that teaches English naturally while players solve challenges.

---

# GAMEPLAY LOOP

Player enters Word Forge

↓

Chooses an Academy

↓

Chooses a Competition Stage

↓

Chooses a Level

↓

Puzzle begins

↓

Read the clue

↓

Look at the letter circle

↓

Connect letters

↓

