# 5. Letter Circle

Every puzzle contains

## 60% Useful Letters

*

## 40% Decoy Letters

Example

```text
G
R
O
U
N
D

W
A
T
E
R

X
Q
B
P
```

Player never knows

* which letters are useful
* which letters are fake
* how many answers still remain

The uncertainty creates challenge.

---

# DECOY LETTERS

Purpose

✓ Prevent instant solving

✓ Encourage exploration

✓ Make every swipe a decision

✓ Increase difficulty naturally

Player should constantly think

> Maybe this word works...

instead of instantly seeing every answer.

