# PLAYER EXPERIENCE

The player should constantly feel

> "I know another word is hiding here..."

That feeling of searching, experimenting, discovering, and finally solving the puzzle is the heart of **Word Forge**. It teaches English naturally while delivering the same sense of progression and accomplishment that makes word puzzle games enjoyable.
